dmxInput

public void dmxInput(java.lang.Integer channelNumber,

Handle DMX Input signals sent by the Universe. All input is assumed to have been validated due to the signal being sent by the Universe class.

Parameters:
channelNumber - Number of the channel for which input has been receieved
channelValue - Value this channel now holds.

assocUpdate

public void assocUpdate(java.lang.Integer firstChannel,
                        java.lang.Integer range)
Handle channel association removal signals sent by Universe. This allows the module to remove its own if appropriate.

Parameters:
firstChannel - The first of the channels being revoked.
range - The range of channels being revoked.
